unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	bRiftBosskilled = true
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(CENTER_MARKER, idSpawned_HellMouth)
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	--Turn on wave1 Spawners; Disable on Wave transfer
	for id, i in ipairs (T_Wave1) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(i)
	end
	
end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	--Wave2
	-- shut down add spawning when the boss dies
	if bRiftBosskilled == false then
		for id, i in ipairs (T_Wave2) do
			Hydra.ActorEnable(i)
		end
	end

end

function Start(sEventName, idActor, nUserParam)

	--Wave3
	if bRiftBosskilled == false then
		-- spawn the adds
		for id, i in ipairs (T_Wave3) do
			Hydra.ActorEnable(i)
		end
		-- Spawn the boss
		for id, i in ipairs (T_WaveBoss) do
			idSpawned_HellMouth = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(CENTER_MARKER, HELLMOUTH_EFFECTGROUP, true)
			Hydra.ActorEnable(i)
		end
	end

end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	N_Wave1Killed = N_Wave1Killed + 1
	
	if N_Wave1Killed >= 8 then
		Hydra.EventSend("Cultist Canyon Rift Wave 1 Complete")
	end
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	N_Wave2Killed = N_Wave2Killed +1
	if N_Wave2Killed >= 3 then
		Hydra.EventSend("Cultist Canyon Rift Wave 2 Complete")
	end
end

bRiftBosskilled = false
